641
01:03:20,099 --> 01:03:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] Do a income, no kids.

642
01:03:22,099 --> 01:03:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] Do a income, no kids.

643
01:03:23,099 --> 01:03:26,099
